{"tid":1797513,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Twitter依家worldwide trend 第一位係 #さ行でXmasの過ごし方がわかる 用嚟做香港文宣","createTime":"2019-12-25T13:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T15:13:35.000Z","uid":221265,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a2de96462d8790e944f3ede2c2af74bff98b2aea","tid":1797513,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:17:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#さ行でXmasの過ごし方がわかる</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8QP1SVf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8QP1SVf.jpg&h=895d62f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實個tag解&quot;用SA行(學過日文應知點解)知聖誕點過<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ESc8xY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ESc8xY&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=9537e62b\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ESc8xY</a><br />\n見佢依家係worldwide twitter trend no.1<br />\n我拋磚用咗明周文化張相tag咗香港抗爭版<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Xy2Cm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Xy2Cm1.jpg&h=14ac10d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>SA: 再見和平的香港<br />\nSI: 依沒有幸福的時代<br />\nSU:對不起義士<br />\nSE:背負未來<br />\nSO: 但仍會戰鬥</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家識日文嘅可自行整個<br />\nor 用Sa Si Su Se So 整英文vers<br />\n tag返<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#さ行でXmasの過ごし方がわかる</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我知有人對我推自己tweet有意見，有人奈post話我食人血饅頭升粉<br />\n唔緊要，歡迎你哋自己做自己vers推自己個tweet<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我做一切嘅目的都係想多啲人知香港嘅事<br />\n之前話我抄tweet copy tweet<br />\n我其實在twitter tag返原作者用日文道咗歉<br />\n<br />\n鬧我無問題<br />\n最緊要大家繼續打twitter！"},{"pid":"4856f2dc28ee9ed41d2b183a3531b156be8ea274","tid":1797513,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HAcZ